						<div class="post_more_img_wrapper">
				<a href="https://lithub.com/the-limitations-of-autobiography-jill-ciment-on-continually-revising-the-past/">
					<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/jill-ciment-1-300x300.jpg" alt=""/>
				</a>
			</div>
						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/the-limitations-of-autobiography-jill-ciment-on-continually-revising-the-past/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">The Limitations of Autobiography: Jill Ciment on Continually Revising the Past</h7>
			</a>
			When author Jill Ciment was seventeen, she had an affair with an art teacher in his forties. Their affair eventually became...			</div>
		</div>
